<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
  <title>Brave UX - Work - Responsum</title>
  <%- include ../partials/_head %>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="wrapper case-study responsum">
    <header class="case-header">
      <div class="case-header-content container">
        <h5 class="case-header-client-name">Responsum</h5>
        <h1 class="case-header-tagline">Helping patients&nbsp;<br />help themselves.</h1>
        <h6 class="case-header-type">Patient Support Platform</h6>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="case-exec-summary padded">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="case-exec-summary-text">We designed an online community where patients of rare conditions can get curated, medically-verified news and support from other patients, all in one place.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-breakdown padded blue">
      <div class="container row">
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Challenge</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            What You Don&rsquo;t Know&nbsp;<br />Could Kill You
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            For rare conditions, online searches invite dead ends, misinformation, and even potentially lethal remedies. And users are often searching on their&nbsp;own.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Solution</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            Curate and&nbsp;<br />Congregate
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            We built an online community around an algorithm that prioritizes medically-accurate articles, tailored to each patient, that can be shared with specialists, loved ones and&nbsp;more.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Scope</p>
          <ul class="case-breakdown-list">
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Information Architecture</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Interaction Design</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block gray">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block column column-block align-self-center half-md">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="1440" data-height="1296">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section1-card1.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-top sr-delay">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section1-card2.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-left">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section1-card3.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-bottom sr-delay">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md column half-md">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-left padded">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Getting to know you</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              With rare conditions, every patient&rsquo;s journey is unique. We created a behavior loop where users get immediate value, while training the algorithm along the way.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block extra-padded off-white">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="1036" data-height="146">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section2-levels.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-left"> 
          <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section2-icon.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-right sr-delay">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block row">
      <div class="inner-block column half-md hide-overflow">
        <div class="inner-box">
          <div class="lazy-ratio full-height" data-width="300" data-height="135">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section3-circle1.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-top">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section3-circle2.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-top">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section3-circle3.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-top">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section3-circle4.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-top">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section3-circle5.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-top">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section3-chart1.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-bottom">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section3-chart2.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-bottom">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section3-chart3.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-bottom">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section3-chart4.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-bottom">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section3-chart5.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-bottom">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-box off-white">
          <div class="lazy-ratio full-height" data-width="693" data-height="324">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section3-reaction1.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-top">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section3-reaction2.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-bottom">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section3-reaction3.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-top">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section3-reaction4.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-bottom">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section3-reaction5.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-top">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block padded column column-block half-md violet">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="608" data-height="784">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section3-tooltip1.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-top">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section3-tooltip2.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-bottom">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>      
    </section>

    <section class="block padded-top gray">
      <div class="inner-block padded-bottom row absolute-center-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content content-centered container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Head and heart</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            Learning about clinical trials doesn&rsquo;t have to feel clinical. We balanced credible resources with warm, comforting design cues.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block row">
        <div class="container-narrow">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop edge-bottom shadow sr-tall lazy-ratio" data-width="1440" data-height="810">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/desktop-3.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block row">
      <div class="inner-block column column-block align-self-center padded half-md hide-overflow pink">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="1116" data-height="1030">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section5-card1.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-stagger-bottom">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/section5-card2.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain absolute sr-stagger-bottom">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md padded column half-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">A clear picture&nbsp;<br />of health</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            On the road to recovery, every detail matters. We created an intuitive workflow that makes it easy for patients to keep track of their treatments, procedures, and visits.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>      
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="2880" data-height="820">
        <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/icons.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded-top gray">
      <div class="inner-block padded-bottom row absolute-center-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content content-centered container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Helping patients take control</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            Setting goals &mdash; and keeping them &mdash; is something any patient can do, to help take back control over their condition. Our UI balances inspirational objectives with customizable progress&nbsp;tracking.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block row">
        <div class="container-narrow">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop edge-bottom shadow sr-tall lazy-ratio" data-width="2732" data-height="1536">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/desktop-1.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/banner.jpg" alt="" class="block-image">
    </section>

    <section class="block row">
      <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md padded column half-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">From living room&nbsp;<br />to waiting room</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            Learning about a condition shouldn&rsquo;t be left at home. Our responsive interfaces let patients bring the articles and issues that matter the most right to their doctor&rsquo;s ppointments, with easily verifiable sources.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block column column-block align-self-center padded half-md hide-overflow teal responsum-mobile">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="frame frame-mobile light sr-left">
            <div class="frame-container">
              <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/mobile-1.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="frame frame-mobile light absolute-bottom sr-right">
            <div class="frame-container">
                <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/mobile-2.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded-top gray">
      <div class="inner-block padded-bottom row absolute-center-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content content-centered container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Care that shares</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            When your condition is one in a million, finding local support is challenging. By providing ways for patients to share, react or follow content, we lay the groundwork for a positive, inclusive and welcoming environment.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block responsum-devices">
        <div class="container-narrow">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop edge-bottom shadow sr-tall lazy-ratio" data-width="1440" data-height="809">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/desktop-2.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
          <div class="frame frame-mobile absolute light sr-left sr-delay">
            <div class="frame-container">
              <img data-normal="./images/work/responsum/mobile-3.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-referral row">
      <div class="inner-block padded column absolute-center-xs half-md blue">
        <div class="container">
          <p class="case-referral-blockquote">To say that Brave UX took our concept to &ldquo;another level&rdquo; doesn&rsquo;t do it justice.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block padded column half-md">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="case-referral-quote-icon"></div>
          <p class="case-referral-text">To say that Brave UX took our concept to &ldquo;another level&rdquo; doesn&rsquo;t do it justice. They took it to another planet, creating an engaging, compelling and truly revolutionary patient engagement platform unlike anything in the healthcare industry. Their discipline, creativity and responsiveness to our vision was exemplary, and their commitment to the unique mission of Brave guided us throughout the entire process.</p>
          <p class="case-referral-author">Andrew Rosenberg, <em>Founder, Responsum</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <%- include ../partials/_footer-scripts %>

</body>
</html>
